setParentTasks

void setParentTasks(java.util.Enumeration pt)
Sets the base or parent tasks of a given task, where the given task is an aggregation expansion of the base tasks. Note that an MPTask contains multiple ParentTasks.

pt - - Enumeration of Tasks which are the "parenttasks"
